#### **Example JSON Schema**
```json
{
    "key": "entity",
    "spec_schema": {
        "type": "array",
        "description": "Entity reference: type, name, required metadata.",
        "minItems": 2,
        "maxItems": 3,
        "items": [
            {"type": "string"},
            {"type": "string"},
            {"type": "string"}
        ],
        "additionalItems": false
    }
}
```

